@baseUrl = https://localhost:7000/api

### Get all employees
GET {{baseUrl}}/employee

### Get employees by department
GET {{baseUrl}}/employee/department/1

### Create employee
POST {{baseUrl}}/employee
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fullName": "Neha Verma",
  "email": "neha.verma@company.com",
  "hireDate": "2024-01-15",
  "departmentId": 1
}

### Deactivate employee
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/employee/1/deactivate
